{"id":232753884,"title":"下半身肥胖該穿什麼去運動？","content":"不知道對不對版，\n頹廢了很久終於開始運動，遇到一個很可笑的問題\n腿太粗了，這是靠我雙腿努力不懈磨出來的洞\nhttps://i.imgur.com/hbA1qc5.jpg\n\n1）短褲直接淘汰，會捲起來\n2）長的棉褲，覺得熱\n3）緊身褲嘛，穿起來太難看\nhttps://i.imgur.com/ZGSWC0m.jpg\n4）我常穿運動褲裙，可以遮掩大腿，可是走路雙腿摩擦會讓內搭褲慢慢地捲起來，雙腿無衣物阻隔直接摩擦很痛的啊 🙄\n（請教大家這麼尷尬的問題會不會太無聊 😅）","excerpt":"不知道對不對版，頹廢了很久終於開始運動，遇到一個很可笑的問題，腿太粗了，這是靠我雙腿努力不懈磨出來的洞，1）短褲直接淘汰，會捲起來，2）長的棉褲，覺得熱，3）緊身褲嘛，穿起來太難看，4）我常穿運動褲裙","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f4388191-41f8-428d-af69-d07d4481dc9e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-24T16:06:42.918Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-24T16:07:07.929Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":5,"tags":[],"topics":["下半身","肥胖","運動"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"運動","forumAlias":"sport","school":"鱼子酱","department":"leanna","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":5}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/hbA1qc5.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/ZGSWC0m.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"b6e2403c-61a3-4970-acf3-f80893ba94d0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/hbA1qc5l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/hbA1qc5l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hbA1qc5l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-24T16:06:42.918Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-24T16:07:07.929Z"},{"id":"b6e2403c-61a3-4970-acf3-f80893ba94d0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/hbA1qc5.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/hbA1qc5","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hbA1qc5l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-24T16:06:42.918Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-24T16:07:07.929Z"},{"id":"9782d54c-c2d2-46b6-bbbf-514d0ee62b7a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/ZGSWC0m.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/ZGSWC0m","thumbnail":"